Fundamental Moombahtonistas include: Dave Nada, DJ Sabo, DJ Melo, Munchi, Uncle Jesse, David Heartbreak, A-Mac, Neki Stranac, Dillon Francis, Sazon Booya, JWLS, Max le Daron, Philadelphyinz (DJ Apt One & Skinny Friedman), Sonido Rampage Y Nader, Billy The Gent, Long Jawns, Obeyah, Cam Jus, Sabbo, Stereo 77, Knife Party, Moombahtron/Riot Earp, EklekTek, Doc Adam, DSTRYD, Porter Robinson, Madd OD, :Dface, Multiplier, DJ Groovematic, The Killabits, Kev Willow,[[Nadia Oh]], Crowd Control and [[Big_Chocolate_(musician)|Big Chocolate]].
Moombahton has also been embraced by influential artists and labels such as T&A Records, Bersa Discos, Mad Decent Records, Fools Gold Records, Dubsided Records, Toy Selectah, Diplo, Ayres, Nguzunguzu, Tittsworth, Laidback Luke, Skrillex, Chuckie, Congorock, RUN DMT, and continues to grow.
